# 位置追踪API测试
# 使用VS Code的REST Client扩展运行这些测试

### 1. 健康检查接口
GET https://localhost:8443/api/location/health
Accept: application/json

### 2. 查询所有位置数据（验证数据是否写入）
GET https://localhost:8443/api/location/list
Accept: application/json

### 3. 上传位置数据 - 北京天安门示例
POST https://localhost:8443/api/location/upload
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
    "deviceId": "test-device-001",
    "latitude": 39.9088,
    "longitude": 116.3976,
    "accuracy": 10.0,
    "altitude": 50.0,
    "speed": 0.0,
    "bearing": 0.0,
    "provider": "gps",
    "locationTimestamp": 1691651400000
}

### 4. 上传位置数据 - 上海外滩示例  
POST https://localhost:8443/api/location/upload
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
    "deviceId": "test-device-002", 
    "latitude": 31.2397,
    "longitude": 121.4999,
    "accuracy": 15.0,
    "altitude": 10.0,
    "speed": 5.2,
    "bearing": 180.0,
    "provider": "network",
    "locationTimestamp": 1691651460000
}

### 5. 测试参数验证 - 缺少必填字段
POST https://localhost:8443/api/location/upload
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
    "deviceId": "",
    "latitude": 39.9088,
    "longitude": 116.3976,
    "provider": "gps"
}

